## Phase 2: Dimensional Modelling (Star Schema)

To optimize analytics and reporting, the raw dataset is transformed into a Star Schema.

| Table            | Columns                          |
| ---------------- | -------------------------------- |
| `dim_date`       | Date, Year, Month, Quarter, Week |
| `dim_location`   | State, City, Location            |
| `dim_restaurant` | Restaurant_Name                  |
| `dim_category`   | Category / Cuisine               |
| `dim_dish`       | Dish_Name                        |


## Why Star Schema?

Reduces duplication and increases clarity

Faster dashboard performance

Consistent business definitions of KPIs

Works perfectly with BI tools like Power BI & Tableau
